data.description: Adorable, pristine 4BR, 2.5 bath home in popular & desirable sidewalk community near parks and recreation. Inviting curb appeal with level front yard and covered front stoop. Oversized backyard is fully fenced and perfect for entertaining and games. Bright cheerful kitchen boasts a sizeable granite island with a breakfast bar and is completely open to family room. Spacious Owner's suite upstairs has large walk-in closet. Two of the other spacious secondary bedrooms have walk-in closets. Laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. Interior has been freshly painted. 2-car garage w/remote control. Home has been lovingly maintained and is in excellent condition. Nearly new - built-in 2020 so all systems and roof only three years old. Homes rarely on the market in this lovely sought -after community in the rising popularity of Dawsonville. Just minutes to fun and exciting Atlanta Motorsport Park; 30 minutes to Chestatee Wild Life Preserve & Zoo; 25 minutes to Amicalola Fall State Park. Elementary , Middle High school just minutes away. This lovely community and area have become home for many happy families. Your family has opportunity to be a part of this lifestyle.
